{"tid":1620014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解政府覺得立蒙面法會嚇到和理非？","createTime":"2019-10-04T09:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T09:13:28.000Z","uid":228203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b4bde3ff4a995a9426e00a95a72bda612cc66c18","tid":1620014,"uid":228203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:13:28.000Z","msg":"自從9月份開始，好多遊行集會都已經無不反對通知書，出得嚟嘅人都會比狗話係參加非法集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家加多條《蒙面法》只係多此一舉，無不反都出嘅人已經有被狗捉嘅覺悟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係林奠仲要引用《緊急法》去立《蒙面法》，開埋D壞先例，咁只會令香港人更加團結，將《反送中》個訴求變成《停用緊急法》/《反蒙面法》，令成個局勢更加惡劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人可以話我知林奠個死人腦諗緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你咁係唔會令到我哋驚㗎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"}]}